    p Rent all the ice you would like, we offer a ton of ice rental options for pick up hockey and parties

    h4 Rental Directions

    p After clicking the button below you will be looking at the schedule for the rink. To adjust your view, hover your mouse over the words "Schedule" on the top left of the page. You can view the schedule by day, week or month. To change to a specific day, click on the calendar on the top left of the page.
